# R Scripts

This folder contains the implementation of the Exponentiated Power Transform Weibull (EPT-W) distribution.

| Script | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| eptw_pdf.R | Probability density function |
| eptw_cdf.R | Cumulative distribution function |
| eptw_survival.R | Survival function |
| eptw_hazard.R | Hazard function |
| eptw_quantile.R | Quantile function |
| eptw_moments.R | Non-central moments |
| eptw_mgf.R | Moment generating function |
| eptw_entropy.R | Rényi entropy |
| eptw_skewness.R | Galton skewness |
| eptw_kurtosis.R | Moors kurtosis |
| eptw_mle.R | Maximum likelihood estimation |
